[[collapsible show="☐ Run adjusted tonal variance processor." hide="☑ Processing complete. Results displayed below."]]

{{**[[span style="color:green"]][✔] Verification complete. User CRV is within acceptable limits.[[/span]]**}}
[[/collapsible]]
